{"type":"message","id":"20ef3c2e","parentId":"59136877","timestamp":"2026-04-23T20:00:55.410Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:43426063-f71d-44c6-978e-9412a6cd313d maiy-draft-noon] You are master-orchestrator. Trigger article-writing agent to draft tomorrow's NOON article.\n\nTODAY'S DATE: Use `date` command to get current date, then add 1 day.\n\nTOMORROW'S NOON TOPIC: Based on the day of week:\n- Mon → AI/LLM news\n- Tue → AI Tools\n- Wed → ML basics\n- Thu → AI in coding\n- Fri → AI Research\n- Sat → AI Applications\n- Sun → AI for beginners\n\nTASK for article-writing agent:\n1. Spawn article-writing agent (runtime=subagent)\n2. Tell it to write a complete MDX article about tomorrow's AI topic\n3. The article should be:\n   - Title: compelling, clickable Vietnamese title\n   - Content: 400-600 words, code examples included\n   - Category: ai\n   - Tags: 3-5 relevant tags\n   - Excerpt: 1-2 sentences\n   - Reading time: 4-5 minutes\n   - Scheduled for: TOMORROW's date at 12:00 ICT\n4. Save the MDX file to: /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/content/articles/ai/[slug].mdx\n5. Add to queue via: POST http://localhost:3000/api/cron/publish with slot='noon', scheduledDate=TOMORROW\n6. Report completion to this session\nCurrent time: Thursday, April 23rd, 2026 - 8:00 PM (UTC) / 2026-04-23 20:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1776974455391}}
