{"type":"message","id":"a775e72e","parentId":"86b5c75b","timestamp":"2026-04-23T20:01:10.478Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Confirmed: Today is Thursday, April 23rd, 2026. Tomorrow is Friday, April 24th, 2026. Topic = AI Research (Friday).","thinkingSignature":"7ff2604bfd35a3377418d6f6351eec7b0d7fcc186cc01a713b4c76b4678b6553"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_imlaa65mm1lt_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"Write a complete MDX article for the MAIY Tech Hub AI knowledge blog.\n\n## TOMORROW'S DATE: 2026-04-24 (Friday)\n## CATEGORY: ai\n## TOPIC: AI Research (Friday = AI Research day)\n\n## ARTICLE REQUIREMENTS:\n1. **Title**: Compelling, clickable Vietnamese title about AI Research\n2. **Content**: 400-600 words, include 1-2 code examples if relevant\n3. **Tags**: 3-5 relevant tags (e.g., research, papers, innovation)\n4. **Excerpt**: 1-2 sentences summary\n5. **Reading time**: 4-5 minutes\n6. **Scheduled for**: 2026-04-24 at 12:00 ICT (noon)\n\n## FILE PATH:\nSave to: /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/content/articles/ai/[slug].mdx\n\nUse a URL-friendly slug like: `ai-research-[something].mdx`\n\n## MDX FRONT MATTER FORMAT:\n```yaml\n---\ntitle: \"Tiêu đề tiếng Việt\"\nslug: ai-research-something\nexcerpt: \"Tóm tắt 1-2 câu\"\ncategory: ai\ntags:\n  - research\n  - papers\n  - innovation\nreadingTime: \"5 phút\"\nscheduledDate: \"2026-04-24T12:00:00+07:00\"\n---\n```\n\n## POST TO QUEUE:\nAfter saving the MDX file, add to queue via:\n```\nPOST http://localhost:3000/api/cron/publish\nContent-Type: application/json\n{\n  \"slot\": \"noon\",\n  \"scheduledDate\": \"2026-04-24\",\n  \"slug\": \"[the-slug]\"\n}\n```\n\n## IMPORTANT:\n- Write in Vietnamese\n- Make it informative and engaging for IT professionals\n- Include practical insights, not just theory\n- Report back the slug and file path when done","label":"article-writing-noon","runtime":"subagent","runTimeoutSeconds":300,"m